review_blob: For some reason even before I bought this beer I new I was gonna love it. You open it pour it or sip out the bottle and ur first thought is how how hoppy and strong it is and within in a second you Just accept this is a amazing beer. Smells great, pours a beautiful hazy brown and taste great. definatly on my top 5 favs

One Of my favorites. High ABV and taste GREAT!
Has A sweet taste that doesnt Cover the "GOOD BEER" taste. I drink it when ever it pops up at a store over here
beer_name: Dogfish Head Midas Touch Golden Elixir
